Package: CoMIT
Type: Package
Title: Coronavirus Monitoring for Inclusivity Tool
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Lia Gale
Maintainer: Ashlie Stephenson <ashlie.stephenson@biofiredefense.com>
Description: CoMIT builds a sqlite3 database from primer and sequence data.
    Primer inputs are submitted via Excel file and then parsed to create a 
    primer table which is used to analyze sequences for mismatches compared 
    to the primers.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
